<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الطّاء والباء والميم<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">بطم:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">البُطْمُ:</span> شَجَرٌ له حَبٌّ مِثْلُ الحَبَّةِ الخَضْرَاءِ، الواحِدَةُ بُطْمَةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
